<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/26737694/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            西风东土的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 33 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7826352">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7826352/" class="title-link">《西风东土》：一次深度寻访中日关系的访学之旅</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7826352"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lmzslh/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1936629-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lmzslh/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">鹿鸣之什</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-03-25"
      class="main-meta">2016-03-25 16:19:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7826352_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  用两天时间读完熊培云六百页的新作《西风东土》，感触很深。觉得自己学识背景不足，不敢评论，只是写一点自己的感想吧。 读过一些些旅日的文章，多是讲日本文化风土的散文类别，日本有哪些好吃好玩的，哪些人情礼节，哪些新鲜资讯，都是偏短小的文字。但是我总觉得这不是真实的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7826352/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">28有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
